My Thai Avatar

📍Thai Glam Studio, Bangkok (Wat Arun Temple)

This was a gifted package in collaboration with Thai Glam Studio. 

@jannie.makeup helped with styling and photography 

It will roughly take a couple of hours so plan your visit accordingly, try to be there in morning to avoid the heat and crowd.

Here’s what you could get in the package of 2500 Thai Baht

🥻Thai costume with full accessories for entire day

💄Make-up and hair by professional artists
 
📸One hour photo session by professional photographer

👜Props like umbrella, bag, flower garland

👡Shoes
